ge all at once with a single tag.<br><br>* Community management<br><br>Groups of all sizes thrive on Discord. In fact, we’re the preferred communication app of game developers, Reddit communities, Twitch streamers, YouTube content creators, and countless other gaming-related interest groups to post news, polls, giveaways, and discussion topics for their thousands of followers.<br><br>* Push notification controls<br><br>Want to be notified when someone DMs or tags you to play Overwatch, but not when there’s a big debate about theorycrafting in your MTG Arena group? That’s easy with our detailed server notification settings, which give you complete control over what types of messages you get alerted for.<br><br>* Cross-platform app for AFK chatting<br><br>Discord is available for both mobile and desktop so you can voice chat with your team while playing games like PUBG, Rainbow Six Siege, or Destiny 2 on your PC, and continue to meme with the whole squad on your phone when you’re out playing Pokemon Go. Have all the flexibility you need in an app that’s fun, sleek, and easy to use.<br><br>Millions of Discord servers have been created so far, with rich communities and tight-knit guilds formed around numerous games and interests. So what are you waiting for? Install Discord for free, start a chat server or join a friend’s, and make yourself at home.<br><br>Have questions or feedback? Email us at support@discordapp.com.', '1661042162367.webp', 'discord-chat-for-gamers', '57M', 'Free', 'Discord Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.discord', NULL, '2', '4.00', '', 1, 0, 0, 11, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2019-11-06 19:53:49', '2022-08-15 14:49:42'),
