(443, 'Offroad 4x4 Car Driving', 'Take control of 9 cars and 2 motorbikes in a huge forest and mountain environment : 16 km² area, 30 km of roads! Accomplish a lot of variety of missions to become a good driver.', NULL, NULL, '!! Offroad car driving Mountain contains 20 levels !!<br><br>Make your choice between city cars, offroad cars, and speed cars.<br>The system of missions is based on popular game play : drive on the map and find one of the 20 spots to launch a mission.<br>The minimap help you to know where are the missions spots.<br><br>The map is very huge, and contains a lot of point of interest. <br>Like a cascade and a lake, a japanese temple, a small airport, different houses and farms, ruins, a camping place, and more... <br>The road system are also very dense, from 2x2 lanes, to very small road of montains, with hill climb.<br><br>Example of missions :<br>- Protect your terrain from wolves<br>- Drive quickly without hitting the boars<br>- Emergency intervention and rescue the victims<br>- Follow your friends through the forest with your 4X4 and SUV<br>- Use your truck to remove all the objects present on the road<br>- Catch all the gangsters before they escape<br>- Finish the course as fast as possible<br><br>Features :<br>- Huge open world, filled with wide open roads, mountains and forests<br>- Realistic driving simulator<br>- Realistic physics<br>- High quality 4x4 vehicles<br>- Dynamic camera angles<br>- Easy to play driving controls, use touch, wheel and tilt controls!<br><br>List of cars : <br>- Dudge Raam 4X4<br>- Aodi A3<br>- Small Cooper<br>- Jeep Wringler<br>- Hammer Alpha 1<br>- Corevete TR1<br>- Ferary 455 Italia<br>- Shuzuki MotorBike GSX650F<br>- Yamahaha 350<br><br>You can adjust the quality button to play without lag.', '1661042172020.webp', 'offroad-4x4-car-driving', '43M', 'Free', 'i6 Games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.i6.mh.offroad', NULL, '2', '4.00', '', 1, 0, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2019-11-22 19:37:14', '2