ou very much for all your support and interest in our games! We would love to hear your suggestions!', '1661042180201.webp', 'stickman-downhill', '47M', 'Free', 'Djinnworks GmbH', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.djinnworks.StickmanDownhill', NULL, '2', '4.00', '', 1, 0, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2019-11-25 20:10:18', '2022-08-15 14:31:26'),
